Class InternalProposal

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agreement_technologies.service.map_planner.InternalProposal

  • public class InternalProposal
extends java.lang.Object
    InternalProposal class represents an agent's plan proposal. This proposal can contain private data, which must be filtered before sending to the other agents.
